m-vt5tCbFM90OODArSZ5zpqQ">Quan định hậu hý tặng - 官定後戲贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/T%E1%BA%A3o-xu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-zn9uhuSQKGzPUdYQv1khSA">Tảo xuân hành - 早春行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ca/poem-r-0sKzn4t1sF64MC4QGgRg">Thạch tướng quân chiến trường ca - 石將軍戰場歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BB%99ng-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-QwR8mfkWimm7tarlC84k4w">Lý Mộng Dương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%A0o/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-uXGoN_DnLq1LcdTVo73uzA">Thuỷ điệu từ kỳ 05 - 水調詞其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author--abLwbhK7CuzmdoZ83_cZw">Trần Đào</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tri%E1%BB%87u-B%E1%BA%AFc-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-TacI7noOI_Sw48zsgX3e4w">Triệu Bắc khẩu - 趙北口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%94ng-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-SNPyNWavNETOARfUuL3nZA">Ông Phương Cương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
